Installation
============

* Install dependencies for npm

```
npm install
```

* Install python dependencies for jinja2

```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```


* And run it!

```
grunt
```



Development
==========

* Install the liveReload plugin for your browser
* Type `grunt` to start watching
* Add any html templates into `app/src/templates/` and they will be automatically compiled into public
* Add any css changes into `app/src/stylesheets/main.scss` and it will be automatically compiled into public
  * You may want to place your variables in app/src/stylesheets/_variables.scss



Production
==========

* Use the contents of `app/public/`